title: V.A. - The Definitive Burt Bacharach Songbook (2006) [mp3@192]

Two CD set that collects 50 of Burt Bacharach's finest songs performed by those that made them hits! Bacharach remains one of the few songwriters that remains just as popular, if not more so, than those that took his songs to the top of the ...    Full Descriptioncharts!
